<p>Every copywriter, marketer or creative director needs a swipe file.</p>
<p>It’s a private place to keep inspiration and references for your work. An ever-growing treasure trove of visuals, ideas, examples and research that fuel your campaign brainstorms, ad concepts and other creative projects.</p>
<p>Back in the day, you’d collect all of it in a physical paper folder. Now, you use mymind.</p>
